    'bitpos:find first bit set or clear in a string'
    'blmove:pop an element from a list, push to another list and return it; or block'
    'blmpop:pop elements from a list, or block until one is available'
    'blpop:remove and get the first element in a list, or block until one is available'
    'brpop:remove and get the last element in a list, or block until one is available'
    'brpoplpush:pop a value from a list, push it to another list and return it; or block'
    'client:manage client connections'
    'cluster:manage cluster'
    'command:get array of Redis command details'
    'config:manage server configuration'
    'copy:copy a key'
    'dbsize:return the number of keys in the selected database'
    'debug:debugging commands'
    'decr:decrement the integer value of a key by one'
    'decrby:decrement the integer value of a key by the given number'
    'del:delete a key'
    'discard:discard all commands issued after MULTI'
    'dump:return a serialized version of the value stored at a key'
    'echo:echo the given string'
    'eval:execute a Lua script server side'
    'eval_ro:read-only variant of EVAL'
    'evalsha:execute a Lua script server side by its SHA1 digest'
